		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="438" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">公子使用手中的邪刃进行3段普攻，第一段与第二段分别造成<span color="#ffacff">25%,35%</span><span>伤害；第三段扔出邪枪，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害；邪枪在前方旋转，持续造成4次</span><span color="#ffacff">15%</span><span>伤害，命中均</span><span color="#72ff96">施加</span><span color="#dc72ff">「断流·雷」</span><span>效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="421" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处在公子近身时，公子使用手中的邪刃先右斩再左斩，各造成<span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害，命中</span><span color="#72ff96">施加</span><span color="#dc72ff">「断流·雷」</span><span>效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="423" height="57" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="汉仪润圆-65W" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">公子在每个玩家处召唤并落下4个雷枪，造成一次<span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ccbfff">断流<span color="#ffffff">效果下，公子使用雷环标记玩家，升空几秒后落在圈的位置，5m内造成</span><span color="#df99ff">100%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，外围造成</span><span color="#df99ff">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧均无效)</span><span color="#ffffff">，命中</span><span color="#ff7272">引爆</span><span>「断流」</span><span color="#ffffff">效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="703" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ccbfff">断流<span color="#ffffff">效果下，公子扔出手中的邪枪，邪枪绕场地滚动，触碰造成</span><span color="#ffacff">40%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，命中</span><span color="#72ff96">施加</span><span color="#dc72ff">「断流·雷」</span><span color="#ffffff">效果，一段时间后邪枪消失。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">公子使用手中的邪枪进行至多5段冲刺，每次均造成<span color="#ffacff">37.5%</span><span>伤害，命中</span><span color="#72ff96">施加</span><span color="#dc72ff">「断流·雷」</span><span>效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处在公子身后时，公子挥转手中的邪枪向后斩击，造成<span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害，命中</span><span color="#72ff96">施加</span><span color="#dc72ff">「断流·雷」</span><span>效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
