		<RichText x="1410" y="927" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ccbfff">断流<span color="#ffffff">效果下，公子移至场地边缘，蓄力召唤一个巨鲸，其跃出造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">75%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，落下造成更大范围的</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span color="#ffffff">，命中均</span><span color="#ff7272">引爆</span><span>「断流」</span><span color="#ffffff">效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1151" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">公子施放数个水喷，呈折线形移动，每个造成<span color="#7fbfff">35%</span><span>伤害，命中</span><span color="#72ff96">施加</span><span color="#72dcff">「断流·水」</span><span>效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="438" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ccbfff">断流<span color="#ffffff">效果下，公子移至场地边缘，蓄力发射一枚巨型水箭，在地面产生4个大范围雨区，随后该处下大雨，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">87.5%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span color="#ffffff">，命中</span><span color="#ff7272">引爆</span><span>「断流」</span><span color="#ffffff">效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1407" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ccbfff">断流<span color="#ffffff">效果下，公子使用邪枪朝玩家发射水枪，随后闪现至其他区域重复此过程1-3次，水枪造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1631" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">公子使用邪枪挥出两道水刃，一水刃偏右，另一水刃偏左，水刃造成<span color="#7fbfff">37.5%</span><span>伤害，命中</span><span color="#72ff96">施加</span><span color="#72dcff">「断流·水」</span><span>效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1407" width="419" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">公子蓄力发射1-3个较粗的水箭，造成<span color="#7fbfff">40%</span><span>伤害，命中</span><span color="#72ff96">施加</span><span color="#72dcff">「断流·水」</span><span>效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
