		<RichText x="1410" y="1631" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当已有的断流被施加不同的断流时，原先存在的断流会被<span color="#ff7272">引爆</span><span>，造成对应元素的</span><span color="#ccbfff">50%</span><span>伤害同时施加新的断流。若断流被引爆技能命中，则正常</span><span color="#ff7272">引爆</span><span>，额外造成对应元素的</span><span color="#ccbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
